{"Code":"038502","Name":"Golden Lotus","Description":"This comfortable 4-star all-inclusive hotel is located directly at one of the clean pebble beaches in Kemer, which are awarded with the blue flag. 400 m from the city centre, the hotel is within walking distance of numerous sights, shopping and entertainment facilities. In the vicinity, guests can find a public transport stop, thanks to which they can explore the surrounding area. Accommodation includes a total of 130 comfortable rooms equipped with air conditioning (hourly, depending on weather conditions), safe deposit box, satellite TV, minibar (free of charge, one-time supply of soft drinks on arrival day), telephone, guest supplies, hair dryer, bath or shower, balcony or shared terrace. The hotel was renovated in 2009. It offers free Wi-Fi access in all areas, including the rooms. High speed internet access can be booked additionally for a fee. The hotel offers a 24h reception where also money can be changed. \nIn the restaurant guests can enjoy the tasty traditional Turkish and also international cuisine. During the live cooking they can watch the preparation of the meals. In addition to soft drinks, local alcoholic drinks and cocktails are served at the bar. The drinks and snacks at the beach bar are extra. \nOn the beach and at the pool, sunbeds, mats and sun protection are available for guests free of charge. Deck chairs on the hotel\u0027s own bathing jetty (available depending on weather conditions) are provided for a fee. Water sports are offered by external organizers for a fee. \nGuests can relax in the SPA centre. Indoor swimming pool, steam bath, sauna, hamam and the fitness room can be used free of charge. Massages and other wellness treatments must be paid separately. \nIn the bookshelf guests will find books to borrow and various games.","Category":"4 STARS","Chain":"","AccommodationType":"Hotel","Destination":"Antalya","District":"Kemer","Address":{"Street":"Deniz Caddesi, 13","PostCode":"7980